<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>A320 Wing Structural Analysis</title>
<script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-300 p-8">

<div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">

<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
A320 Wing Structural Analysis
</h1>

<p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">
Computational analysis of aerodynamic loading and structural response of a tapered aircraft wing.
</p>

<!-- Results -->
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-8 text-center">
    <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded">
        <p>Max Moment</p>
        <p class="font-bold text-white">~2.2 MN·m</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded">
        <p>Max Stress</p>
        <p class="font-bold text-white">~88 MPa</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded">
        <p>Yield</p>
        <p class="font-bold text-white">300 MPa</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-800 p-4 rounded">
        <p>FoS</p>
        <p class="font-bold text-white">~3.4</p>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Images -->
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
    <img src="images/stress.png" class="rounded">
    <img src="images/bending.png" class="rounded">
</div>

<!-- Method -->
<h2 class="text-2xl text-white mb-2">Methodology</h2>
<p class="mb-6">
Elliptical lift distribution was used. Shear force and bending moment were computed using numerical integration.
A variable spar model was used and stress calculated using beam theory.
</p>

<!-- Insight -->
<h2 class="text-2xl text-white mb-2">Key Insight</h2>
<p class="mb-6">
Wing taper improves structural efficiency by reducing stress towards the tip while concentrating material at the root.
</p>

<a href="index.html" class="text-sky-400">← Back</a>

</div>

</body>
</html>
